  "detailed_description": "Based on my Half-Life mod from years ago, Vampire Slayer: The Resurrection is a new asymmetric first-person hero shooter where the slayers have traditional weapons and the vampires rely on speed, strength and stealth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188960/extras/6c73d5e129eca48fbf640c14020fb94c.poster.avif?t=1693986928\" width=618 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188960/extras/6c73d5e129eca48fbf640c14020fb94c.webm?t=1693986928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188960/extras/6c73d5e129eca48fbf640c14020fb94c.mp4?t=1693986928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Only the Slayers Carry Weapons. The Vampires have stealth, speed and deadly melee attacks. <br>Slayers must knock a vampire to the ground before staking them. If they do not stake them within a few seconds the Vampire will resurrect.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188960/extras/7b8c2c0a6569012c8cece2ca9f244fdd.poster.avif?t=1693986928\" width=618 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188960/extras/7b8c2c0a6569012c8cece2ca9f244fdd.webm?t=1693986928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188960/extras/7b8c2c0a6569012c8cece2ca9f244fdd.mp4?t=1693986928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A Vampire can feed from dead Slayers to regain strength. Leap from tall buildings onto your prey or hunt in the dark.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188960/extras/085f3cec815e7e510e48e3c8bdde26ae.poster.avif?t=1693986928\" width=618 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188960/extras/085f3cec815e7e510e48e3c8bdde26ae.webm?t=1693986928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188960/extras/085f3cec815e7e510e48e3c8bdde26ae.mp4?t=1693986928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Now YOU must choose a side.",
